        	<h1>Why yoga is good for absolutely everything...</h1>
        	        		<p class="synopsis">Practising yoga can help you lose weight, manage health problems and keep you at the top of your mental peak</p>
        	        	
        	<ul class="details">
									<li>By Kate Birch, Editor, Aquarius</li>
								    	    	    									<li>Published: 09:23 November 29, 2011</li>
								
				    	    		    		    		
			
		
			    	    									<li class="source"><a href="http://gulfnews.com/about-gulf-news/al-nisr-portfolio/aquarius" title="Aquarius"><img title='Aquarius' alt='Aquarius' src='/polopoly_fs/aquarius-1.5467!image/383078356.gif_gen/derivatives/article_credit/383078356.gif' /></a></li>
