	    	<li >
		      <a href="http://gulfnews.com/life-style/motoring/test-drives/lexus-takes-on-germany-s-top-saloons-1.1010197" title="Lexus takes on Germany's top saloons">
  	            <img src="/polopoly_fs/lexus-gs-350-vs-bmw-535i-vs-mercedes-e-350-1.1010820!image/4142077372.jpg_gen/derivatives/box_58/4142077372.jpg" alt="Lexus GS 350 vs BMW 535i vs Mercedes E 350">
		      </a>
		      <h6><a href="http://gulfnews.com/life-style/motoring/test-drives/lexus-takes-on-germany-s-top-saloons-1.1010197" title="Lexus takes on Germany's top saloons">Lexus takes on Germany's top saloons</a></h6>
		      
		      		      	<p>Can the new GS 350 can match the Germans in performance?</p>
			  
